title: Berner and Ampachino - Traffic
description:
Traffic album for sale by Ampichino / Berner was released Apr 21, 2009 on the Bern One label. Berner and Ampichino collaborate on Traffic, which takes the listener into the high stakes and high risk world of the drug trade. Traffic buy CD music This is the perfect follow up to Devilz Rejects and Drought Season. Production by Cozmo, Joe Millionaire, Gennesse, Mid Wes.
